{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-04-27-09-07-tree-and-git-projects/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ohmybuck"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c9474cfb-7292-596d-ad9f-6021a7b951e4","excerpt":"Tree prints out directory structures via the terminal. Install it with The following will print out files in the current project structure, ignoring files in…","html":"<p>Tree prints out directory structures via the terminal.</p>\n<p>Install it with</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> tree</code></pre></div>\n<p>The following will print out files in the current project structure, ignoring files in the <code class=\"language-text\">.gitignore</code> file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> ls-tree -r --name-only HEAD <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> tree --fromfile</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Tree And Git Projects","date":"April 27, 2020","description":"Tree And Git Projects"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-04-27-09-07-tree-and-git-projects/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-04-27-09-02-node-current-directory/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Node Current Directory","draft":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-05-23-14-48-env-file-checker/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Env File Checker","draft":null}}}}}